* Documentation in ReStructured Text markup is inside source/

* Python Sphinx should be installed to create PDF, HTML, etc.::

    sudo aptitude install python-sphinx python-sphinx-rtd-theme

* Some examples. From docs/ directory::

    # Make PDF doc. (needs LaTeX installed): output will be in build/latex
    make latexpdf

    # Make HTML doc." output will be in build/html
    make latexpdf
